Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.68,0:00:21.49,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找尋著看不見的明天 著急地用手觸摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.64,0:00:25.99,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.15,0:00:38.54,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來是沒有出口的迷宮 就像需要解謎的拼圖一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.20,0:00:49.81,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有奇跡出現   夢想也將成為勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.05,0:00:54.98,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart  在荏苒的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.13,0:00:57.90,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你的憧憬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.05,0:01:00.40,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just my Love  因為那份思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.56,0:01:03.69,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我了無形的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.93,0:01:09.77,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像稍微感受到了迷惘和煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.77,0:01:11.33,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論在什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.48,0:01:14.71,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart  在荏苒的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.49,0:01:23.63,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just my Love  對你的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.67,0:01:28.64,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.08,0:21:40.35,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在心中綻放的玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.50,0:21:47.19,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗中燃盡  僅是一束火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.47,0:21:55.82,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在滿是隔閡的街上 如遊戲般的迷失自我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.97,0:22:00.08,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以小丑的心情躊躇著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.94,0:22:08.42,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要踐踏悲傷的殘片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.57,0:22:12.80,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人在未來中戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.37,0:22:20.93,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以解開今晚的謎底仍然是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.21,0:22:25.43,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up！真面目  Hurry up！回到從前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.80,0:22:32.98,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is passion　兩個人的手中充滿的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.14,0:22:39.95,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入黑暗之中  想緊緊擁抱住陽光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.40,0:22:45.50,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在迷宮中相互Kiss
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.61,0:22:54.50,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁向樂園  僅差一道門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.70,0:00:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續新的一年的旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.40,0:00:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,困難的案件仍然與日俱增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.30,0:00:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天柯南進入第二個年頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.30,0:00:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南馬上遇到了大危機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.10,0:00:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.90,0:00:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.00,0:00:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.30,0:00:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.30,0:01:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江戶川柯南誘拐事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.10,0:01:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.20,0:01:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有沒有聽我說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.60,0:01:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯什麼嗯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.20,0:01:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從你爸爸媽媽把你寄放到我們家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.00,0:01:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後調動工作去國外已經很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.00,0:01:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你一點都不寂寞嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.70,0:01:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.00,0:01:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.60,0:01:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這父母是怎麼當的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.40,0:01:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒露過面不說 連聯絡都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.00,0:02:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.40,0:02:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謊言快要被拆穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.40,0:02:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我真正的父母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.50,0:02:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的確去了國外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.90,0:02:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不算全是謊話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.70,0:02:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得當初是阿笠博士把他交給我們的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.30,0:02:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣的話我們向阿笠博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.80,0:02:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要他父母的聯絡方式會比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.60,0:02:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行啊 不可以這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.80,0:02:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.90,0:02:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有什麼事情怕我們聯絡你父母後會被拆穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.40,0:02:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.30,0:02:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得趕快想個辦法才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.90,0:02:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不然我工藤新一的身份就要被揭穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.60,0:02:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.40,0:02:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她來了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.00,0:02:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.80,0:02:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.80,0:02:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人一定很寂寞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.70,0:02:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.60,0:02:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來跟媽媽一起回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.90,0:02:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.10,0:02:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.20,0:02:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這孩子真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.20,0:02:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又在鬧彆扭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.10,0:02:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實這都要怪我們一直把他丟在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.90,0:03:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是江戶川文代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.50,0:03:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是江戶川柯南如假包換的母親喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.90,0:03:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.30,0:03:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,江戶川柯南只是我編的假名字而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的人物根本不可能有母親的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.90,0:03:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子多虧你們照顧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.80,0:03:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後我會再答謝你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.20,0:03:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我等著喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.20,0:03:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.20,0:03:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.60,0:03:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了那邊要寫信回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.80,0:03:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.90,0:03:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝禮千萬別忘了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.40,0:03:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye Bye 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.00,0:03:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大嬸 你到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.80,0:03:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才不是說過我是你母親嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.10,0:03:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我的母親是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.80,0:03:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤有希子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.30,0:03:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.80,0:03:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的母親就是那個會迷倒全世界男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.90,0:03:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在19歲得到所有的大獎之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.40,0:04:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就成為了日本頭號美女明星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.10,0:04:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是她跟年輕的小說家工藤優作相愛後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.30,0:04:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20歲就結婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.50,0:04:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是她急流勇退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.10,0:04:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來就生了一個兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.50,0:04:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是現在卻把兒子丟在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.40,0:04:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟她那個世界級的推理小說家丈夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤優作一起到國外旅行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.60,0:04:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.10,0:04:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是她的獨生子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.70,0:04:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.00,0:04:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這個人就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.50,0:04:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逼我吃藥讓我身體變小的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.10,0:04:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣男人的同夥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可別亂動哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.50,0:04:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是乖乖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.90,0:04:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大嬸就帶你到一個好地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.90,0:04:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裏可有趣多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.10,0:04:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 會不會開車啊 快給我讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.10,0:04:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來人 抓住那個孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.40,0:05:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.50,0:05:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們怎麼會知道我的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.40,0:05:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.40,0:05:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在卡拉OK包廂殺人事件裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.90,0:05:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我用過工藤新一這個名字的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.80,0:05:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那個事件以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.90,0:05:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們說不定從哪裏得知本來應該被殺死的我還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.20,0:05:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.40,0:05:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明明交代警部不要洩露我的名字的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.10,0:05:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.60,0:05:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是我的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.70,0:05:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.20,0:05:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到蘭那裏告訴她一切嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.80,0:05:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.60,0:05:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在回到那裏的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭他們一定會有危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.70,0:05:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.20,0:05:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.80,0:05:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.70,0:05:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 被他逃掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.70,0:05:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太大意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.70,0:05:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我猜那個小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.20,0:05:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定就是工藤新一錯不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.60,0:05:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.70,0:05:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道真的變小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.30,0:05:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻給我去找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他到警方那裏的話就麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.00,0:06:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是到哪裏去找呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.50,0:06:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他下一個會去的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.70,0:06:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定是那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.40,0:06:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是先找知道整個事情的阿笠博士商量商量吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.70,0:06:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是博士還真慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.40,0:06:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候他會去哪裏散步啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.70,0:06:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.80,0:06:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博…士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.80,0:06:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先睡一下吧 小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.43,0:06:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.10,0:06:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是廚房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.10,0:06:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.80,0:06:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的頭到現在還是暈暈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.70,0:06:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.10,0:06:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.10,0:06:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她趁我失去意識的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.60,0:06:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我帶到這棟房子的二樓來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你還沒把他給殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.10,0:06:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就別為難我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.20,0:06:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是上級的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.90,0:07:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那個女的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站在她面前的那個人是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.20,0:07:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.00,0:07:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上級說他的藥物副作用是個特例
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.00,0:07:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以必須把他帶回組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.10,0:07:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來她是因為這個才沒殺我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那個男的是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.40,0:07:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.20,0:07:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個戴面具的男的怎麼這個樣子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.50,0:07:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.10,0:07:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他往這裏來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.80,0:07:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個小鬼起來了沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.00,0:07:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有 我看藥力大概還沒過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.40,0:07:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.60,0:07:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裏面那個真的是高中生偵探工藤新一嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到現在還不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.50,0:07:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.20,0:07:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤新一失蹤的那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.10,0:07:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟這小子出現在那個事務所的日子是一致的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.20,0:07:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且在這之後發生在這小鬼周圍的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.50,0:07:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都圓滿地解決了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.80,0:07:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想這一定是組織新開發的那種藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.30,0:07:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他的身體變小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我也來做做試驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.50,0:08:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.10,0:08:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,組織開發的那種新藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.60,0:08:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在出來的時候也帶了一點在身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.50,0:08:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只要讓別人吃下這種藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.00,0:08:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就知道它能不能讓人變小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.00,0:08:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要讓誰吃這種藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.70,0:08:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是明天要跟我們交易的那個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.90,0:08:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,組織不是早就說過交易一結束就要我們把他解決了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.00,0:08:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正好拿這個來試驗一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.50,0:08:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道這個藥能讓人變小之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.30,0:08:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.90,0:08:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之先把和我們交易的那個男的殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.80,0:08:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後再把這個小鬼給解決掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是跟你說過了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.60,0:08:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,組織要調查這個小鬼身上的副作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.60,0:08:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上級已經命令我要把他帶回去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.30,0:08:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道組織秘密的人還能讓他活著嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.80,0:08:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.60,0:08:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.60,0:08:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經決定這麼做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.60,0:08:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是再囉嗦的話這裏只會再多一具屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.80,0:08:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.30,0:08:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.10,0:09:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天交易的地點你告訴那個男的了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.90,0:09:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是用我們的老方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.60,0:09:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交易時間在13點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.70,0:09:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在可以好好睡一覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.30,0:09:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個都睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.40,0:09:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個男的還戴著面具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.60,0:09:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看了就覺得恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.80,0:09:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得先把繩子解開逃出去才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.10,0:09:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有個紅酒的酒瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.31,0:09:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.40,0:09:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用毯子包著酒瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.90,0:09:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他們有沒有聽到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.70,0:09:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒聽到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.20,0:09:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 趁現在用瓶子的碎片把繩子割斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.60,0:09:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然繩子解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.60,0:09:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是要怎麼從2樓這裏出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.00,0:09:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面雖然有積雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.30,0:09:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是從這裏跳下去還是太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.30,0:09:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看還是躲到冰箱裏去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.00,0:10:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.00,0:10:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才敲碎的酒瓶流出來的酒好像流到那裏去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.60,0:10:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.90,0:10:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.70,0:10:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個小鬼不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.20,0:10:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我醒來的時候他就不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.00,0:10:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是從窗子逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.60,0:10:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.20,0:10:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是利用積雪從這裏跳下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.50,0:10:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他休想逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.90,0:10:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.10,0:10:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點去找那個小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.50,0:10:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.70,0:10:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個小鬼還在這房間裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.20,0:10:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.50,0:10:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他讓我們以為他已經逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.90,0:10:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實他就躲在這裏等我們離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.90,0:10:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.70,0:10:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,納命來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.80,0:10:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼搞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.60,0:11:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你猜錯了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.10,0:11:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正這個小子也沒地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.90,0:11:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等今天的交易結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.00,0:11:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們再把他找出來 到時候再解決他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.10,0:11:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為我要完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.50,0:11:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.30,0:11:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒有發現地毯下面的儲物室的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.30,0:11:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.20,0:11:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.90,0:11:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就趁現在把那種藥找出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.90,0:11:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 到處都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.30,0:11:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是能知道那種藥的成分的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.50,0:11:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定就能知道讓我身體復原的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.20,0:11:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少阿笠博士是這麼說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.90,0:11:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是他們把藥全都帶到交易的地方去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.80,0:11:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這張報紙是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面到處都是洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.90,0:11:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們跟交易對象聯絡的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.80,0:12:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是把報紙上面的字剪下來貼成一封信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.60,0:12:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.60,0:12:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們剛才不是說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.00,0:12:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要把交易的那個人給解決掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.50,0:12:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.60,0:12:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得趕快找出他們交易的地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.20,0:12:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阻止殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.40,0:12:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並且把藥拿到手才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.60,0:12:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據報紙上剪下部分的上下文推測
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.60,0:12:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,い て ほ べ ル カ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.20,0:12:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這些字重新組合就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.10,0:12:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,べいカほてル(米花大飯店)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.80,0:12:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是米花大飯店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.90,0:12:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是光有這些還是不知道會在飯店裏的什麼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.40,0:12:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該還有其他文字的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.80,0:12:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 到處都找不到切除過的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.10,0:12:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是刀子的印子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.80,0:12:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.80,0:12:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被切除掉的那個數字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.30,0:12:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是這一頁上面的8月份的月曆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.10,0:12:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.90,0:12:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有切痕的是9月27號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.90,0:12:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那對應的8月份的日子就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.90,0:12:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米花大飯店30
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.70,0:13:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裏就是他們交易的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.00,0:13:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是米花大飯店30是哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.70,0:13:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這家飯店只有19層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.80,0:13:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又沒有30號房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.40,0:13:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,19號是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.90,0:13:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 請您稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.50,0:13:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.40,0:13:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是儲物櫃的號碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.70,0:13:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.40,0:13:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸把鑰匙牌弄丟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.40,0:13:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是30號的櫃子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.40,0:13:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30號是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.90,0:13:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.80,0:13:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏寄放的物品只到26號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.00,0:13:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.40,0:13:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 到底是哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.50,0:13:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.20,0:13:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經12點多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.70,0:13:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們交易的時間是13點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.90,0:13:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 我把錢包忘在車子裏面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把車子停在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.80,0:13:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在42號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.90,0:13:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我馬上就回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.00,0:13:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停…停車場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.60,0:14:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停在30號車位上的是這輛車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.80,0:14:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說他們會在車子裏交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.50,0:14:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過裏面好像沒人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.80,0:14:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.40,0:14:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想對我的車子幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.50,0:14:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 這個人一定是小偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.80,0:14:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.50,0:14:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 你們誤會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.00,0:14:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是覺得這輛車子很漂亮 所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.00,0:14:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事好像跟他們無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來也不是這裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.50,0:14:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好高大的男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.20,0:14:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在看什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.50,0:14:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在看停車場的車位號碼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.20,0:14:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在30這裏用粉筆寫了個小小的1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.90,0:14:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 301的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.00,0:14:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該就是這個飯店的房間號碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.90,0:14:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後剛才那個大個子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.20,0:14:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該就是那些傢伙的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.80,0:14:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交易對象了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.50,0:15:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個戴面具的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.80,0:15:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏果然是他們的交易地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.60,0:15:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那個女的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.70,0:15:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.70,0:15:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被包夾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.10,0:15:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次被抓的話肯定會被殺掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被那個戴面具的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.50,0:15:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.40,0:15:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.80,0:15:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 正男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.10,0:15:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這扇門會自動上鎖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.60,0:15:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只要把門關上就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.40,0:15:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託你看家囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.10,0:15:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.00,0:15:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你來晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.40,0:15:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.20,0:15:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是什麼壞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.20,0:15:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了追一個從藍波星球來的宇宙壞蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.30,0:15:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才到這個星球來的宇宙偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.60,0:15:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.50,0:15:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明明就是小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.20,0:15:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了要掩人耳目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.20,0:15:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才會扮成小孩子的模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.50,0:15:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你變回原來的樣子讓我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.70,0:15:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.70,0:15:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是個小偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.80,0:16:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.80,0:16:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你等著 我叫員警來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.10,0:16:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 正男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.10,0:16:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽他的話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.90,0:16:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是媽媽的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.40,0:16:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是藍波星球的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.20,0:16:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以發出任何聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.90,0:16:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.10,0:16:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是宇宙偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.50,0:16:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到竟能用這個變聲器蒙混過關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.60,0:16:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事要我幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.50,0:16:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先我想借用這房間裏的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.20,0:16:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你身上有沒有口香糖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.50,0:16:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有是有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 你要幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.40,0:16:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.20,0:16:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把你們點的酒和菜送來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.30,0:16:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒點過這些啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.30,0:16:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我明明接到電話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.70,0:16:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.30,0:16:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.60,0:16:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.80,0:16:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫他送到裏面來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.80,0:16:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.70,0:16:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.70,0:16:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點送到裏面來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.90,0:16:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 送進去吧 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.90,0:16:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦 你不要生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.20,0:17:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還磨蹭什麼 快滾出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.50,0:17:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,口香糖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.70,0:17:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就先來乾杯好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.90,0:17:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.90,0:17:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還要來介紹另外一位客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外一位客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.60,0:17:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說那個小鬼在這裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.50,0:17:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 根本就沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這輛推車只是個障眼法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.30,0:17:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實他是在這個衣櫥裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.00,0:17:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.90,0:17:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.20,0:17:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.20,0:17:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是他是什麼時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.20,0:17:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁著他叫來的服務生跟我們說話的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.20,0:17:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把口香糖黏在鎖孔上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.80,0:17:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使得門不能自動上鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.30,0:17:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後趁我們的注意力全在這輛推車上的時候偷偷溜進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.40,0:17:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我會上你的當嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.40,0:17:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.90,0:18:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今只有用手錶型麻醉槍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.50,0:18:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能發射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.10,0:18:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那個有趣的手錶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.60,0:18:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早在抓到你的時候就做了手腳 讓它報廢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.20,0:18:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.30,0:18:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了陰曹地府之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.10,0:18:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再去後悔你太小看我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.50,0:18:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高中生偵探工藤新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.90,0:18:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.20,0:18:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒明白嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.70,0:18:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.90,0:18:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界首屈一指的推理小說家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.50,0:18:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤優作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.50,0:18:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.20,0:18:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這個大嬸難道就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.40,0:18:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 小新
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.10,0:18:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.50,0:18:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 連我兒子也沒有發覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.50,0:18:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可見我這個女演員的演技還沒有退步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.30,0:18:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說這個大個子就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.50,0:18:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.50,0:18:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿笠博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.20,0:18:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要生氣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.70,0:18:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸媽媽實在太擔心你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.90,0:18:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 小新
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.30,0:19:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們好不容易回家一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.80,0:19:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是卻發現你不在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.30,0:19:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.30,0:19:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們聽阿笠博士說了我變小的事情之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.90,0:19:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就設計出這麼可惡的惡作劇來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.30,0:19:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是測試你的偵探能力而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.40,0:19:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.10,0:19:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個優秀的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.00,0:19:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然跟著我們留下來的線索找到這裏來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.10,0:19:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我剛才開槍之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.30,0:19:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都在我的預料之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.40,0:19:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我那個時候躲在廚房的儲物室裏面你們也知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.40,0:19:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.40,0:19:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要當偵探的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.90,0:19:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還要多多努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.80,0:19:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這都怪你自己沒注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.00,0:19:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最近剛出了一本新的小說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.40,0:19:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我扮的就是裏面的 黑暗男爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.40,0:19:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 不是這樣子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.30,0:19:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為自己要被殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.60,0:19:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.10,0:19:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你還是儘快離開這個這麼危險的國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.30,0:19:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟爸爸媽媽一起到國外去生活 怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.00,0:19:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 小新
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實就是因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.50,0:19:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道你自己現在的處境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才會這樣安排的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.20,0:20:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是因為這樣才會幫你爸爸媽媽演戲的 新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.60,0:20:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有個朋友在國際刑警組織裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.80,0:20:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我拜託他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.10,0:20:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以請他幫我們調查那個組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.10,0:20:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信很快就可以拿到那種藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.50,0:20:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的身體也可以很快恢復正常了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.80,0:20:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.50,0:20:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種危險的偵探遊戲就到此為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.40,0:20:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.70,0:20:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我自己的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.00,0:20:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要自己來解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.10,0:20:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你們不要插手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.70,0:20:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小新
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.20,0:20:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.30,0:20:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還不能離開日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.70,0:20:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.80,0:20:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.90,0:20:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就暫時讓他自己做喜歡做的事情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.10,0:20:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.60,0:20:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你聽好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.40,0:20:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有危險的話我馬上就帶你去國外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.40,0:20:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且依我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.70,0:20:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不肯離開這裏還有別的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.90,0:20:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你兒子還要寄放在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.00,0:20:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我這兒子說什麼也不肯離開這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.50,0:20:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是夫人…這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.30,0:20:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.00,0:21:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我兒子的養育費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.90,0:21:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要的時候儘管從裏面提出來用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.10,0:21:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1000萬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.10,0:21:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您兒子這麼可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.60,0:21:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也都非常喜歡他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.70,0:21:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有 蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.60,0:21:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個孩子就麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.80,0:21:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看這個孩子好像很喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.10,0:21:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.60,0:21:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我記住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.80,0:23:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太有意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.50,0:23:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不枉我這次扔下稿子回到日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.20,0:23:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是小新不會有事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.70,0:23:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.60,0:23:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要不了多久就會找我們哭訴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.10,0:23:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我們環遊世界一周你看怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.20,0:23:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.20,0:23:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在那裏 在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.60,0:23:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工藤先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.60,0:23:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是外國雜誌社的那些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.60,0:23:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會出現在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.00,0:23:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的兒子打電話給我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.78,0:23:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼剩下的308頁什麼時候給我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.20,0:23:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 是我先來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.28,0:23:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是在這裏等了很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.28,0:23:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被暗算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.48,0:23:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.70,0:23:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.40,0:23:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看這間房間裏一定被人裝了黃色炸藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.90,0:23:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對錯不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.60,0:23:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悲情的犯行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.40,0:24:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這把刀子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.00,0:24:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是良二幹的好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.30,0:24:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.40,0:24:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.90,0:24:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,堀田三兄弟殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.40,0:24:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.60,0:24:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化學肥料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.50,0:24:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一集的兇手真是出人意料
